Class BioactiveEntityEnricherStatisticsWriter

  • java.lang.Object
    • psidev.psi.mi.jami.enricher.listener.impl.writer.EnricherStatisticsWriter<T>
      • psidev.psi.mi.jami.enricher.listener.impl.writer.InteractorEnricherStatisticsWriter<BioactiveEntity>
        • psidev.psi.mi.jami.enricher.listener.impl.writer.BioactiveEntityEnricherStatisticsWriter
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    EventListener, BioactiveEntityEnricherListener, EnricherListener<BioactiveEntity>, InteractorEnricherListener<BioactiveEntity>, AliasesChangeListener<BioactiveEntity>, AnnotationsChangeListener<BioactiveEntity>, ChecksumsChangeListener<BioactiveEntity>, IdentifiersChangeListener<BioactiveEntity>, InteractorChangeListener<BioactiveEntity>, XrefsChangeListener<BioactiveEntity>
    public class BioactiveEntityEnricherStatisticsWriter
extends InteractorEnricherStatisticsWriter<BioactiveEntity>
implements BioactiveEntityEnricherListener
    A statistics logger which records changes made by the enricher. Each addition, removal or update is counted and, upon the completion of the enrichment of the object, is logged in either a file of successes or failures depending on the enrichmentStatus.
    Since:
    08/08/13
    Author:
    Gabriel Aldam (galdam@ebi.ac.uk)
